longBusinessSummary: HyperBlock Inc., a crypto-asset company, owns and operates cryptocurrency datacenters in North America. Its product offerings include cryptocurrency mining, Mining-as-a-Service, server hosting, and server hardware. The company is based in Toronto, Canada.
